arStrings.szText: Is it true? About the runaway. I heard they found his body. I heard it was spirits, of all things, that killed him!
Can’t say for sure. But I do know his mother wouldn’t appreciate you prying about it.
Oh, you are right, Coyo. Gossip rots the mind.
But, if you really want to know... then I might tell you to travel the eastern roads, south of lower Kurast. I might mention it’s there the corpse lies.
